<div class="row">
<div class="col-lg-6 order-2 order-lg-1 align-self-center">
<div class="text-area text-white">
<h2>Hızlı ve Kolay bir<br>
bankacılık deneyimi!</h2>

<p>MobilDeniz ile bankacılık işlemleri 7/24 cebinizde!</p>

<div class="buttons">
<div class="row ">
<div class="col-lg-6"><a class="btn btn-gradient color btn-block" href="https://app.tr.adjust.com/99l558q?deeplink=mobildenizyeni%3A%2F%2Fscreen%3FmenuKey%3DDigitalCustomerInfo&amp;fallback=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.denizbank.com%2Fdijital-bankacilik%2Fmobil-deniz">MobilDeniz'i İndir</a></div>

<div class="col-lg-6 d-none d-lg-block"><a class="btn btn-outline-white btn-block" href="/dijital-bankacilik/mobil-deniz">Detaylı Bilgi</a></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

